# Build-context trim. Copied to the repo root at deploy time (`cp infra/.dockerignore .dockerignore`).
# NOTE: this only affects what gets baked into images / build-context size. It does NOT influence
# Docker Compose's runtime ${...} interpolation of the repo-root .env — that hazard is handled by
# running all prod compose commands from infra/ (see infra/deploy/README.md).
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
.git
**/.env
!**/.env.example
!**/.env.production.example
**/coverage
**/.dev-storage
apps/mobile
docs
*.png
